00:20:45,077 --> 00:20:47,955
‐ Huh?
‐ Well, sure. Of course I was.

513
00:20:47,955 --> 00:20:49,999
I was worried
you might get upset with me,

514
00:20:49,999 --> 00:20:51,584
you being a Dollar and all.

515
00:20:51,584 --> 00:20:54,879
‐ Oh, really? I'm glad
I proved you wrong, then.

516
00:20:54,879 --> 00:20:56,839
<i>♪ ♪</i>

517
00:20:56,839 --> 00:20:58,591
‐ You were there that other day.

518
00:20:58,591 --> 00:20:59,717
Weren't you?

519
00:20:59,717 --> 00:21:01,177
‐ Th‐there?
Where's that?

520
00:21:01,177 --> 00:21:03,345
‐ When we were getting thrashed
by Kadota's guys.

521
00:21:03,345 --> 00:21:05,556
‐ Yeah, we saw you
at the deserted factory

522
00:21:05,556 --> 00:21:07,558
with the Black Rider, right?

523
00:21:07,558 --> 00:21:09,351
‐ Since we're not wearing
our yellow scarves,

524
00:21:09,351 --> 00:21:12,229
we caught you
with your pants down, didn't we?

525
00:21:12,229 --> 00:21:13,773
