526
00:21:13,773 --> 00:21:17,651
MAN: That morning, Ruri Hijiribe
was delivered safely to her home

527
00:21:17,651 --> 00:21:20,738
by a transporter
on a black bike.

528
00:21:20,738 --> 00:21:24,074
RURI: Uh, um, thank you
so much for doing this.

529
00:21:24,074 --> 00:21:26,911
So, about your fee...

530
00:21:28,078 --> 00:21:30,331
‐ This one's on the house.

531
00:21:30,331 --> 00:21:31,248
‐ Huh?

532
00:21:31,248 --> 00:21:33,626
‐ I actually enjoyed myself.

533
00:21:33,626 --> 00:21:35,753
After all,
I almost never get the chance

534
00:21:35,753 --> 00:21:37,963
to meet someone
with special powers like you

535
00:21:37,963 --> 00:21:39,423
in this city.

536
00:21:39,423 --> 00:21:41,217
‐ How'd you know?

537
00:21:41,217 --> 00:21:43,511
‐ Somehow, I could sense it.

538
00:21:43,511 --> 00:21:46,597
You could say you give off
the same "scent" as me.

539
00:21:46,597 --> 00:21:48,724
‐ Hold on.
Are you trying to say

540
00:21:48,724 --> 00:21:50,768
that you're‐‐
that all of those rumors

541
00:21:50,768 --> 00:21:52,812
I've been hearing on TV
are true?

542
00:21:52,812 --> 00:21:54,063
You aren't human?

543
00:21:54,063 --> 00:21:55,648
‐ No.

544
00:21:57,691 --> 00:21:59,026
‐ [gasps]

545
00:22:03,155 --> 00:22:05,950
‐ [laughing]

546
00:22:07,451 --> 00:22:09,662
MAN:
That was when it struck her‐‐

547
00:22:09,662 --> 00:22:11,747
that this was a vast world.

548
00:22:11,747 --> 00:22:15,584
Even phantoms and monsters
could enjoy life.

549
00:22:15,584 --> 00:22:17,002
RURI: Even me.

550
00:22:17,002 --> 00:22:18,462
Even Yuhei!

551
00:22:18,462 --> 00:22:20,965
Even that Headless Rider!

552
00:22:20,965 --> 00:22:22,424
Why?

553
00:22:22,424 --> 00:22:25,511
All this time...
why didn't I realize?

